1 technical assistance; requiring the Unit to establish a certain specialized team to
2 provide certain direct assistance to certain agencies Executive Departmental Units
3 under certain circumstances; requiring the Unit to establish and maintain a
4 dashboard with certain information on its website submit a certain annual report by
5 a certain date each year; authorizing certain unredacted cybersecurity findings to be
6 viewed by certain individuals; and generally relating to the establishment of the
7 Audit and Finance Compliance Unit in the Department of Budget and Management.
